ollection includes single printed maps and blueline prints and photocopies of printed or manuscript single maps and may also include some multi-sheet single maps, plates from atlases, books or periodicals, and printed facsimiles. These maps may also show various subjects, such as recreation and tourism. To request a specific map or for more information, contact a reference librarian in the Geography & Map Division (202) 707-6277 or through the \"Ask a librarian\" link through the Geography & Map Division website https://ask.loc.gov/map-geography/. Title supplied by cataloger. Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:17:51.023Z", "group": ["gmd/multimap", "catalog-split-08", "catalog", "multimaps", "main-catalog-split-08"], "hassegments": true, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2022589354/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:ak:-0:51:ak-051:ak-051-02-01/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:ak:-0:51:ak-051:ak-051-02-01/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=996&w=1110", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:ak:-0:51:ak-051:ak-051-02-01/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=1993&w=2220"], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["nome", "united states", "kodiak", "alaska"], "mime_type": ["image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["2025-06-07t11:32:21.500000", "sheet", "2022589354", "2022-12-08t17:53:11"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map", "collection"], "other_title": ["Alternate supplied title: Alaska title collection--drawer 51", "Alternate supplied title: Alaska title collection--cities and towns Kodiak-Nome"], "partof": ["catalog", "cities and towns", "single sheet maps, title collection", "general maps", "geography and map division"], "score": 30.471327, "shelf_id": "G4374 coll .M3 drawer 51", "site": ["catalog"],